metadata.name: Nouns Map 1
metadata.description:
World map for nouns community

This product is designed to create a world map for nouns projects. It allows users to customize their Discord server into nations, regions, or cities, and link their usernames with a geographic location. The interactive map lets users explore and discover various nouns projects, uncovering new and exciting things.

Moreover, users can create custom maps, adding their own locations and sharing them with friends and peers. This world map offers endless possibilities, providing an engaging way to interact with the nouns project.
